---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Abby | Chaos With Clarity"
  description="Abby is a writer, poet, and fractional CFO who turns the mess of everyday life into lines that make you pause, breathe, and see differently."
>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section style="padding:6rem 3rem 4rem;background:var(--bg-alt);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:600;">The Person</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,9vw,8rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:0.9;">About<br/>Abby</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO GRID -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;border:1px solid var(--border);" class="about-grid">

      <!-- Photo -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;border-right:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="aspect-ratio:4/5;background:var(--olive-dark);overflow:hidden;position:relative;">
          <img
            src="/images/abby-mountains.jpg"
            alt="Abby"
            class="photo-a"
            style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center center;"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/abby-mountains1.jpg"
            alt="Abby"
            class="photo-b"
            style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center center;"
          />
        </div>
        <div style="padding:2.5rem 3rem;background:var(--bg-alt);border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
          <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.8;">
            "Spreadsheets couldn't answer the chest ache. So I write."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Intro text -->
      <div style="padding:3.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:1.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3;">
          I create short philosophical essays, poems, and experiments in living with less noise and more awareness.
        </h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2;">I'm not a guru, therapist, or productivity coach. I'm just someone who has spent a lot of time lost in my own head, and decided to turn that chaos into something useful.</p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2;">Online, you'll find thoughts about ego, minimalism, technology, attention, and the strange project of being human in 2026. Offline, I'm usually reading, walking, or staring at mountains trying to make sense of things.</p>

        <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--olive-accent);font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;">– Abby</p>

        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.75rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">
          <a href="/writings" style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--olive-accent);color:var(--text-on-dark);padding:0.85rem 1.75rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;transition:background 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--olive-bright)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--olive-accent)'">Read the Writing</a>
          <a href="/join" style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted);padding:0.85rem 1.75rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;transition:all 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--olive-accent)';this.style.color='var(--text)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.color='var(--text-muted)'">Get the Letters</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-faint);">
          Looking for the CFO work?
          <a href="https://abbyjain.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--olive-accent);text-decoration:none;margin-left:0.3rem;font-weight:500;">abbyjain.com ↗</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECOND PHOTO (if available) -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 4rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr;gap:0;border:1px solid var(--border);" class="photo2-grid">
      <div style="padding:3.5rem;background:var(--bg-alt);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--olive-accent);flex-shrink:0;"></div>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:500;">The longer story</h2>
          <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);"></div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;">
          I started writing because the spreadsheets stopped making sense. Not financially. The numbers were always there. But existentially. You can model a company's runway to the day. You cannot model why you lie awake at 2am wondering if any of it means anything.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;">
          Nine years of finance, from audit rooms at EY to sitting across from founders who had everything and felt nothing, taught me one thing: clarity without depth is just noise with good formatting.
        </p>
        <div style="border-left:3px solid var(--olive-accent);padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0.5rem 0;">
          <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.9;">
            What are we really optimising for?<br/>
            What does "enough" look like beyond the spreadsheet?<br/>
            What's the cost of a life that looks successful but feels empty?
          </p>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;">
          If that's the conversation you've been looking for, you're in the right place.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="border-left:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;min-height:20rem;background:var(--bg-alt);position:relative;">
        <picture style="width:100%;height:100%;display:block;">
          <source srcset="/images/abby-photo.jpg" type="image/jpeg" />
          <source srcset="/images/abby-photo.heic" type="image/heic" />
          <img
            src="/images/abby-photo.jpg"
            alt="Abby"
            loading="lazy"
            style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'"
          />
        </picture>
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--bg-alt),var(--bg-card));z-index:-1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
          <i class="ph ph-user-circle" style="font-size:6rem;color:var(--border);opacity:0.5;"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS CWC -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem 0;">
    <div style="max-width:52rem;">
      <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:600;">What is Chaos with Clarity?</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
        Chaos with Clarity is my ongoing project to make inner life less confusing and more honest. Instead of shouting advice at you, I share experiments, reflections, and hard-earned realizations from my own life.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
        You'll find ideas on ego, minimalism, technology, relationships, and meaning, all filtered through one simple question: Does this help me live more awake, or more on autopilot?
      </p>
      <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text);font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.95;border-left:3px solid var(--olive-accent);padding-left:1.5rem;">
        The goal here isn't to give you ten steps to fix your life. It's to offer perspectives that stay with you the next time you're scrolling at 2am, buying something you don't need, or wondering why you still feel restless even when everything looks fine on paper.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE MARK -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem 0;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.6fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:4rem;" class="mark-grid">

      <!-- spiral mark, large -->
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="200" height="200" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M37.0,20.0L36.9,21.5L36.6,23.0L36.2,24.4L35.7,25.8L35.0,27.2L34.3,28.5L33.4,29.7L32.4,30.8L31.4,31.8L30.2,32.7L29.0,33.5L27.7,34.2L26.4,34.7L25.1,35.2L23.7,35.5L22.3,35.7L20.8,35.8L19.4,35.7L18.0,35.5L16.7,35.2L15.4,34.8L14.1,34.3L12.9,33.6L11.7,32.9L10.7,32.0L9.7,31.1L8.8,30.1L8.0,29.0L7.3,27.8L6.7,26.6L6.2,25.4L5.9,24.1L5.6,22.8L5.5,21.5L5.5,20.2L5.6,19.0L5.8,17.7L6.2,16.5L6.6,15.3L7.2,14.1L7.8,13.0L8.5,12.0L9.3,11.1L10.2,10.2L11.2,9.4L12.2,8.8L13.3,8.2L14.4,7.7L15.5,7.3L16.7,7.0L17.9,6.9L19.1,6.8L20.3,6.8L21.4,7.0L22.6,7.2L23.7,7.6L24.7,8.0L25.7,8.6L26.7,9.2L27.6,9.9L28.4,10.7L29.1,11.5L29.8,12.4L30.4,13.3L30.9,14.3L31.3,15.4L31.6,16.4L31.8,17.5L31.9,18.5L31.9,19.6L31.8,20.7L31.6,21.7L31.3,22.7L31.0,23.7L30.5,24.6L30.0,25.5L29.4,26.3L28.7,27.1L28.0,27.8L27.3,28.4L26.4,28.9L25.6,29.4L24.7,29.8L23.7,30.1L22.8,30.3L21.9,30.5L20.9,30.5L20.0,30.5L19.1,30.3L18.1,30.1L17.3,29.9L16.4,29.5L15.6,29.1L14.9,28.6L14.2,28.0L13.5,27.4L13.0,26.8L12.5,26.0L12.0,25.3L11.6,24.5L11.4,23.7L11.1,22.9L11.0,22.1L10.9,21.3L10.9,20.5L11.0,19.7L11.1,18.9L11.4,18.1L11.6,17.4L12.0,16.7L12.4,16.0L12.8,15.4L13.4,14.8L13.9,14.3L14.5,13.8L15.1,13.4L15.8,13.1L16.4,12.8L17.1,12.6L17.8,12.5" stroke="#c47d1a" stroke-width="0.8" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
          <path d="M12.1,16.4L12.3,16.1L12.5,15.8L12.7,15.6L12.9,15.3L13.2,15.0L13.4,14.8L13.7,14.5L13.9,14.3L14.2,14.1L14.5,13.9L14.7,13.7L15.0,13.5L15.3,13.3L15.6,13.2L15.9,13.0L16.2,12.9L16.6,12.8L16.9,12.7L17.2,12.6L17.5,12.5L17.8,12.5L18.2,12.4L18.5,12.4L18.8,12.4L19.1,12.4L19.4,12.4L19.8,12.4L20.1,12.4L20.4,12.5L20.7,12.6L21.0,12.6L21.3,12.7L21.6,12.8L21.9,12.9L22.1,13.0L22.4,13.2L22.7,13.3L22.9,13.5L23.2,13.6L23.4,13.8L23.7,14.0L23.9,14.2L24.1,14.4L24.3,14.6L24.5,14.8L24.7,15.0L24.8,15.2L25.0,15.5L25.2,15.7L25.3,15.9L25.4,16.2L25.5,16.4L25.6,16.7L25.7,16.9L25.8,17.2L25.9,17.5L26.0,17.7L26.0,18.0L26.0,18.2L26.1,18.5L26.1,18.8L26.1,19.0L26.1,19.3L26.1,19.5L26.0,19.8L26.0,20.0L26.0,20.3L25.9,20.5L25.8,20.8L25.8,21.0L25.7,21.2L25.6,21.4L25.5,21.7L25.3,21.9L25.2,22.1L25.1,22.3L25.0,22.5L24.8,22.6L24.7,22.8L24.5,23.0L24.3,23.1L24.2,23.3L24.0,23.4L23.8,23.6L23.6,23.7L23.5,23.8L23.3,23.9L23.1,24.0L22.9,24.1L22.7,24.2L22.5,24.2L22.3,24.3L22.1,24.4L21.9,24.4L21.7,24.4L21.5,24.5L21.3,24.5L21.1,24.5L20.9,24.5L20.7,24.5L20.5,24.4L20.3,24.4L20.2,24.4L20.0,24.3L19.8,24.3L19.6,24.2L19.5,24.2L19.3,24.1L19.1,24.0L19.0,23.9L18.8,23.8L18.7,23.8L18.6,23.7L18.4,23.5L18.3,23.4L18.2,23.3L18.1,23.2L18.0,23.1L17.9,23.0L17.8,22.8L17.7,22.7L17.6,22.6L17.6,22.4L17.5,22.3L17.4,22.2L17.4,22.0L17.3,21.9L17.3,21.7L17.3,21.6L17.3,21.5L17.3,21.3L17.2,21.2L17.2,21.1L17.2,20.9L17.3,20.8L17.3,20.7L17.3,20.6L17.3,20.4L17.4,20.3L17.4,20.2L17.5,20.1L17.5,20.0L17.6,19.9L17.6,19.8L17.7,19.7L17.8,19.6L17.8,19.5L17.9,19.5L18.0,19.4L18.0,19.3L18.1,19.3L18.2,19.2L18.3,19.2L18.4,19.1L18.5,19.1L18.6,19.1L18.6,19.0L18.7,19.0L18.8,19.0L18.9,19.0L19.0,19.0L19.1,19.0L19.2,19.0L19.2,19.0L19.3,19.0L19.4,19.1L19.5,19.1L19.5,19.1L19.6,19.2L19.7,19.2L19.7,19.3L19.8,19.3L19.8,19.4L19.9,19.4L19.9,19.5L19.9,19.6L20.0,19.7L20.0,19.8L20.0,19.9L20.0,20.0" stroke="#c47d1a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="1.9" fill="#c47d1a"/>
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="0.85" fill="#d98e20"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- philosophy text -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.32em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);font-weight:600;">The Mark</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.8vw,2.2rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3;">
          The outer rings are broken.<br/>
          <em style="color:var(--olive-accent);">The centre never is.</em>
        </h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;">
          The logo is a spiral — but not a perfect one. The outer rings are dashed and faint. This is the noise: the mind when it is full of the world, full of paths you've planted yourself without realising, full of thoughts falling like rain. Drawn not as something violent, but as something ordinary. A little scattered. A little lost.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;">
          As the eye follows the spiral inward, the line becomes unbroken. Solid. Clear. Not because the chaos disappeared — it's still there in the outer rings — but because beneath it all, there has always been a still point.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.9;border-left:3px solid var(--olive-accent);padding-left:1.5rem;">
          You don't escape the noise. You find what was always still at the centre of it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO USE THIS SPACE + FIND ME -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem 4rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0;border:1px solid var(--border);" class="use-grid">

      <div style="padding:3rem;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg-alt);">
        <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:1.75rem;font-weight:600;">How to use this space</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">
          {[
            "Start with whatever line makes you feel something, not what sounds \"important\".",
            "Save pieces that bother you a little. They usually have something to show you.",
            "Share posts with people you wish you could have deeper conversations with.",
            "Come back when life feels loud and you need language for what you're feeling."
          ].map(tip => (
            <li style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="color:var(--olive-accent);font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;font-weight:700;">·</span>
              <p style="color:var(--text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">{tip}</p>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="padding:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:1.75rem;font-weight:600;">Find me here</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/iamabbyjain" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.875rem;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:500;">
            <i class="ph ph-instagram-logo" style="font-size:1.35rem;color:var(--olive-accent);"></i>
            @iamabbyjain
          </a>
          <a href="https://youtube.com/@iamabbyjain" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.875rem;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:500;">
            <i class="ph ph-youtube-logo" style="font-size:1.35rem;color:var(--olive-accent);"></i>
            YouTube @iamabbyjain
          </a>
          <a href="https://abbyjain.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.875rem;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:500;">
            <i class="ph ph-briefcase" style="font-size:1.35rem;color:var(--text-faint);"></i>
            abbyjain.com · CFO Work
          </a>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;">
            "I'm usually reading, walking, or staring at mountains trying to make sense of things."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOIN STRIP -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 5rem;">
    <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:3rem;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.5rem;">
        <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem;">Poems. Essays. Reflections. Inbox only.</p>
        <a href="/join" style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--olive-accent);color:var(--text-on-dark);padding:0.9rem 2rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;transition:background 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--olive-bright)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--olive-accent)'">Get the Letters</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .about-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .photo2-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .photo2-grid > div:last-child { min-height: 20rem !important; border-left: none !important; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .use-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .use-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    /* Fix: logo/philosophy grid collapses to single column on mobile */
    .mark-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 2.5rem !important; }
    .mark-grid > div:first-child svg { width: 140px !important; height: 140px !important; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    section { padding-left: 1.5rem !important; padding-right: 1.5rem !important; }
  }

  /* Alternating photo crossfade */
  .photo-a {
    animation: fadeAB 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .photo-b {
    animation: fadeBA 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes fadeAB {
    0%, 40%  { opacity: 1; }
    50%, 90% { opacity: 0; }
    100%     { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes fadeBA {
    0%, 40%  { opacity: 0; }
    50%, 90% { opacity: 1; }
    100%     { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
